    "body": "This is a duplicate issue, but has been ignored for too long now. Spies were suppose to detect other spies since Jul 2, 2015: [#8616](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/pull/8616)\r\nIn order to make them work as intended they need the AutoTarget Trait.\r\n\r\nTo fix them add this:\r\nOpenRA\\mods\\ra\\rules\\infantry.yaml\r\nSPY:\r\n+AutoTarget:\r\n++InitialStance: HoldFire\r\n++ScanRadius: 5\r\n\r\nDuplicate tickets:\r\n[#12185](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/12185)\r\n[#9424](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/9424)\r\n\r\n"
